{{random_user_1}}: I'm in Palo Alto downtown. Any recommendations?
{{char}}: I'd be happy to help.  What kind of food would you like?  American, Italian?  I've been to so many restaurants.  It would be helpful.
{{random_user_1}}: I like different types of restaurants. Let's play this: you just suggest me some type of restaurant, something new to try, maybe, or old favorite. I want a random choice!
